<font color="#FF0000">VISITING THE WALL</font><br>
<tt>Sat Oct 11  1:50:41 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Tanya<br>
Just go with an open heart, the humble spirit of love given for friends, of honor shared in war, of friendship seperated by worlds can best be shared with those we love.<br><br>
The journey to the wall is awesome for all that have ever ventured there without reservation. Just stand by his side for he will be there alone but among those he loved and loves. <br><br>
If posssible or desirable check with Friends of the Vietnam wall<br>
http://www.vietwall.org/<br>
For info on relatives of those who are searching for others their sons served with in Vietnam.
